        Media captionFleeing through flames: "I'm so scared right now... so terrified"Looting was also reported in the southern fire area over the weekend.Luxury homes in Malibu and other beach communities are among the properties razed by the flames.Hollywood actor Gerard Butler shared a picture of a charred house on Twitter, writing: "Returned to my house in Malibu after evacuating. Heartbreaking time across California." He thanked firefighters for their "courage, spirit and sacrifice". 
    
        
